ellipse 0.34,0.48 0.06,0.05 stroke #3a6018
ellipse 0.66,0.50 0.06,0.05 fill #4e7a28 0.78
ellipse 0.66,0.50 0.06,0.05 stroke #3a6018

# Bottom group
ellipse 0.42,0.68 0.06,0.08 fill #5a8a30 0.82
ellipse 0.42,0.68 0.06,0.08 stroke #3a6018
ellipse 0.58,0.70 0.06,0.08 fill #4e7a28 0.8
ellipse 0.58,0.70 0.06,0.08 stroke #3a6018
ellipse 0.50,0.74 0.05,0.07 fill #6a9a38 0.78
ellipse 0.50,0.74 0.05,0.07 stroke #3a6018

# Hop cone scale detail (tiny lines on a few cones)
